7
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,079
That's very thoughtful.

8
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:34,079
Thank you.

9
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,400
My condolences.

10
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,720
She knew her husband was like this,

11
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:49,250
