15
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,000
It's subconscious resistance.

16
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:04,040
Then why is she so calm?

17
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:04,840
What else?

18
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,560
