174
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:45,800
It is useful.

175
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:46,960
Very useful.

176
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,000
It's useful.

177
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,440
Thank you.

178
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,640
